# Project — reference clones of the upstream firmware + PC GUI repos.
# Tracked in their own git histories (gitlab.../xense/tc-gu-01[-pc].git),
# NOT as submodules — this SDK only depends on the wire protocol they
# define, not on their build artefacts. Clone-on-demand for development;
# see README.md "Firmware / PC GUI reference repos".
